item.title: Need help with compiler!
item.dc:creator: @masterp00n masterp00n
item.description:
@masterp00n wrote:

i fixed it…i downloaded pimpscape and i put
for compiler:

@echo off title server Compiler "%ProgramFiles%\Java\jdk1.6.0\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java pause
and for runserver:

@echo off title Runserver set java="C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0\bin\java.exe" java -Xmx1024m -cp .;./jython.jar;./MySql/mysql-connector-java-3.0.17-ga-bin.jar server pause
